data.description: A charming 3 bed, 1.5 bath towhome in Las Vegas is now for sale! Featuring a 2 car garage and a cozy front patio where you can enjoy a relaxing evening! Come inside to discover an inviting dining & living area w/tile flooring and neutral palette throughout. The gorgeous kitchen is comprised of wood cabinetry w/granite counters, a pantry, stainless steel appliances, and an island complete w/a breakfast bar & butcher block counters. Perfectly-sized bedrooms w/ample closets! Did I mention the brand new roof?! Keep cool during the summer months by dipping into the refreshing Community pool! Located close to the heart of Vegas, this is sure to be the home for you, don't miss out! Sellers willing to negotiate lower price if buyer's don't need appliances, etc.
